<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
	<title>Site Error</title>
	<meta name="robots" content="noindex,noarchive" />
	<style type="text/css">
		*,
		:after,
		:before {
			-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
			-moz-box-sizing: border-box;
			box-sizing: border-box
		}

		html {
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		body {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			font-size: 87.5%;
			line-height: 1.42857;
			font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
		}

		html,
		body {
			height: 100%;
		}

		.cch-page {
			height: 100%;
			position: relative;
			background-color: #f0f0f0;
		}

		.cch-downtimeNotice {
			position: relative;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 40rem;
			border-top: 1.875rem solid #00aac8;
			border-bottom: .625rem solid #ca5699;
			background-color: #fff;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 1.25rem 1.875rem 1.875rem;
		}

		h1,
		h2 {
			padding: 0;
			line-height: 1.25;
			font-weight: normal;
		}

		h1 {
			margin: 0;
			color: #00aac8;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}

		h2 {
			margin: 1.25rem 0 0 0;
			font-size: 1rem;
			color: #ca5699;
		}

		p {
			margin: 0 0 .625rem;
			padding: 0;
			color: #565a5c;
		}

			p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

		a,
		a:link,
		a:visited {
			color: #00aac8;
		}

			a:hover {
				color: #0096b0;
			}

			a[href^="tel"] {
				white-space: nowrap;
			}

			a[href^="tel:"]:before {
				content: "\260e";
				margin-right: 0.5em;
			}

		.img-logo {
			display: block;
			margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		}

		@media print, screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
			h1 {
				font-size: 1.75rem;
			}

			h2 {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
			}

			.cch-downtimeNotice {
				top: 15%;
				max-width: 45rem;
				padding-left: 16rem;
				background-image: url("/includes/org/img/childrens-logo.png");
				background-position: 1.25rem 1.25rem;
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
			}

			.img-logo {
				position: absolute;
				top: 1.25rem;
				left: 1.25rem;
			}

			a[href^="tel:"] {
				color: #565a5c;
				text-decoration: none;
			}

				a[href^="tel:"]:before {
					content: none;
					margin-right: 0;
				}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="cchPage" class="cch-page">
		<div id="cchDowntimeNotice" class="cch-downtimeNotice">
			<img class="img-logo" src="/includes/org/img/childrens-logo.png" alt="Cincinnati Children's Logo">
			<h1>Wait a minute. That wasn't supposed to happen!</h1>
			<p>
				We apologize for the inconvenience, but our server has encountered an error while attempting to show you the page you requested.
			</p>
			<p>
				We have recorded the error and our staff will review the report so we can fix the problem as soon as possible -- hopefully by the time you return to view this page again.
			</p>
			<p>
				In the meantime, you can try to visit our <a href="/">home page</a> or use our <a href="/search?q=&start=0&site=entire-site">search engine</a>.
			</p>
			<h2>If You Need to Contact Us</h2>
			<p>
				If you need to contact Cincinnati Children's Hospital Medical Center, you can always call our main switchboard at <a href="tel:1-513-636-4200">513-636-4200</a> or <a href="tel:1-800-344-2462">1-800-344-2462</a>.
			</p>
			<div id="time"></div>
			<div id="server"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script>
		const client = new XMLHttpRequest();
		client.open("GET", "/errorpage.html", true);
		client.send();

		client.onreadystatechange = function () {
			if (this.readyState === this.HEADERS_RECEIVED) {
				var servervalue = client.getResponseHeader("CCHMCServer");
				document.getElementById("server").innerHTML = '(' + servervalue + ')';
			}
		}

		document.getElementById("time").innerHTML = new Date(Date.now()).toLocaleString();
	</script>
</body>
